# Checkout & Payment Test Cases

## Scope
Covers checkout flow, order validation, payment handling and error behavior.

---

## TC_CHK_001 – Successful Checkout with Valid Card
Priority: Critical  
Expected: Order completes successfully, confirmation page shown, email sent.

---

## TC_CHK_002 – Declined Payment Card
Priority: Critical  
Expected: User sees friendly decline message, order NOT created.

---

## TC_CHK_003 – Empty Cart Checkout Attempt
Priority: High  
Expected: Action blocked with message: "Cart is empty"

---

## TC_CHK_004 – Refresh During Checkout
Priority: Medium  
Expected: Cart persists, no data loss.

---

## TC_CHK_005 – Duplicate Payment Protection
Priority: Critical  
Expected: System prevents double charging.

---

## TC_CHK_006 – Network Failure Handling
Priority: High  
Expected: Retry option + safe fail behavior.

---

## TC_CHK_007 – Saved Card / Token Payment
Priority: High  
Expected: Token validated securely, no sensitive data exposed.
